		- desmall
		- texture2tga
		- nbfs2tga
		- ncgr2tga
		- cbgt2tga
		- cdpth2tga
	- Bump version number to be in sync with xoreos

Monday, 2014-10-20 (Version 0.0.0)
	- Created a dedicated repository for the tools

Sunday, 2012-07-22 (Version 0.0.0-pre)
